Yesterday, Netflix's Blood and Water made its debut and people already want more. The series, that is the second original African series from Netflix, definitely won people over. Blood and Water is about a Cape Town teen, Puleng, played by Ama Qamata, that's on a mission to find her sister, Phume. Young actors like Natasha Thahane, Thabang Molaba and Arno Greeff are on the cast as well. Tweeps were so impressed by the first season, they cannot wait for the second season. Read:Â CICI GIVES BIRTH TO BOY           